{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 859741565, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 14:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859741157,45974302,1815]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64814547]y被讨厌的勇气[/uid] (2026-03-02 14:44):[/b]<br/><br/>狼王 印度和越南怎么看 现在国内很多都在越南建厂[/quote]<br/>看啥 化工类 稀土类吗？<br/>那是原材料收益和第一次精炼，半成品还是要回国精炼的", "lou": 1020, "content_length": 75, "reply_to": 859741157, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772434013}, {"pid": 859742352, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 14:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859741934,45974302,1816]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64814547]y被讨厌的勇气[/uid] (2026-03-02 14:49):[/b]<br/><br/>因为我是认证机构的，对接都是比较大的国内场   越南建厂大部分是生产线之类的 因为那边人工低[/quote]<br/>一个是人工低 当时更重要的是环保没人管啊。。。。", "lou": 1021, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 859741934, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772434344}, {"pid": 859743085, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 14:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859742640,45974302,1816]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64814547]y被讨厌的勇气[/uid] (2026-03-02 14:54):[/b]<br/><br/>对 中国人口红利没有那么明显了  所以我才说印度或者越南在走我们的来时路  是否有啥可以提交埋伏？[/quote]<br/>你说的是实业还是什么？实业的话那边需要有带路人 不然外地人做不了的 不管是矿还是场地你都没机会<br/>我在南边只有一个稀土提炼厂的参股 还是别人给的 我觉得那边能赚钱的人都不简单。", "lou": 1022, "content_length": 169, "reply_to": 859742640, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772434641}, {"pid": 859743633, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 64, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 15:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "4000多下跌  今天拿科技类还能做到红的 就是胜利 如果还能把仓位降下来<br/>那就是胜利中的胜利<br/>但是不能清仓科技啊 不然一轮动就SB了 <br/>注意我说的比例 至少上半年我认为都没问题<br/>开会前就是稳指数了  整体问题不大 开会前没有指数级别风险的定调不变 。", "lou": 1023, "content_length": 216, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772434880}, {"pid": 859744185, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 15:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859743785,45974302,1817]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64814547]y被讨厌的勇气[/uid] (2026-03-02 15:02):[/b]<br/><br/>想问的是个股[s:ac:赞同][/quote]<br/>那我不知道 我对化工类知道的很少<br/>我上学时候学化学只会配平化合价和等价交换", "lou": 1024, "content_length": 75, "reply_to": 859743785, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772435097}, {"pid": 859745487, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 15:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我还是之前的判断 资源类我是这么个排序 这里说的是我对之后的预期 <br/>石油最强 天然气 甲醇次之  贵金属再次之  小金属能源金属再再次之   化工我不懂 太细分了 要去看涨价线  最后是稀土要做长线", "lou": 1025, "content_length": 164, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772435648}, {"pid": 859749033, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 15:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859748600,45974302,1820]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=437522]trustsky[/uid] (2026-03-02 15:33):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大黄金现在是什么预期？可以长线吗[/quote]<br/>我是长线", "lou": 1026, "content_length": 13, "reply_to": 859748600, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772437007}, {"pid": 859786454, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-02 20:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "天然气大起飞", "lou": 1027, "content_length": 12, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772455716}, {"pid": 859819211, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 80, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 08:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "提前说一下  昨天三桶油全部涨停 是 护盘+机构避险+量化+散户追涨的合力<br/>但是整体大资金应该是净流出的，护盘和机构这两天肯定会跑，带动量化也会跑，所以千万不要发了疯今天去追这种超大市值的石油 <br/>这是真的会死的。", "lou": 1029, "content_length": 195, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772496794}, {"pid": 859821686, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 08:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=859821015,45974302,1833]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64814547]y被讨厌的勇气[/uid] (2026-03-03 08:36):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大今天还有票子能进的吗[s:ac:吓][/quote]<br/>我觉得很多啊 资源还有很多没涨的 或者没加速的化工原料  科技还有一大堆涨价的被昨天干下来了 那不是继续能做了<br/>做这些比追石油海运贵金属要安全多了。", "lou": 1030, "content_length": 141, "reply_to": 859821015, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772498573}, {"pid": 859822079, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 53, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 08:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "还有国算那些机构也没跑路 他们吹了那么久还没有完全出货哪里可能结束<br/>然后就是埋伏十五五题材等开会后兑现的卫星和核聚变那些<br/>还有长期趋势的半导体设备 AI硬类的各种上游细分。<br/>这个市场机会很多的啊 你们要善于找低位 而不是追高位", "lou": 1031, "content_length": 210, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772498790}, {"pid": 859824777, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 42, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 09:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正你们记得科技+资源就行了 细分前面也说了很多次<br/>为什么这么配经过这段时间你们应该也了解了。<br/>炒股长期复利才是最重要的。", "lou": 1032, "content_length": 115, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772500181}, {"pid": 859825541, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 09:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "天然气板块[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1033, "content_length": 8, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772500547}, {"pid": 859828323, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 09:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "给我封测道歉[s:ac:反对]", "lou": 1034, "content_length": 10, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772501828}, {"pid": 859830600, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 09:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "新高兑现有点猛 控一下仓位。", "lou": 1035, "content_length": 26, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772502786}, {"pid": 859830751, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-03 09:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天唯一开盘有点机会的只有我今早说的 天然气。其他没什么机会", "lou": 1036, "content_length": 58, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772502845}, {"pid": 859832806, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 41, "score_